===Etymology 2===
[[Dialect|Dia(lect)]] + [[phone]]
====Noun====
'''diaphone'''

#{{linguistics}} A particular [[dialect]]al variant of a [[phoneme]].
#All the dialectal variants of a phoneme, considered as a whole.
{{wikipedia2|diaphone (linguistics)}}
